activate(bytes8).details: Applications linked to active risks may be underwritten

add(bytes8).details: add a new risk to a product registered with this instance

deactivate(bytes8).details: Applications linked to paused/archived risks may not be underwritten

initialize(address,address).details: This initializer needs to be called from the instance itself.

isConsumingScheduledOp().details: Returns true only in the context of a delayed restricted call, at the moment that the scheduled operation is being consumed. Prevents denial of service for delayed restricted calls in the case that the contract performs attacker controlled calls.

linkPolicy(uint96,bytes8,uint96).details: links a policy to its bundle

setAuthority(address).details: Transfers control to a new authority. The caller must be the current authority.

unlinkPolicy(uint96,bytes8,uint96).details: Unlinks a policy from its risk.
